Change 127.0.0.1 to development in the hostfile

on my mac localhost is bound to both ::1 and 127.0.0.1. Using a specific
hostname that is only bound to 127.0.0.1 ensures that the binding is no
issue for the webserver.

Add env files for CLJS, make swagger work

The most important thing to remember is to bind the HTTP server to
the IP address that the hostname resolves to. 127.0.0.1 is not the same
as ::1 when it comes to binding, so localhost resolved to ::1 for the
webserver and 127.0.0.1 for the browser.
